		<region region-id="1885" left="174" top="6417.75" width="531.75" height="9.75" align-x="183.75" align-y="6426" show-border="false" show-highlight="false" is-protected="true" z-order="0" background-color="inherit" tag="">
			<text use-page-width="false" push-down="false" lock-width="true">
				<p style="普通" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit">
					<b>Mos选型的额定电流值需按流过MOS电流的2~3倍余量以上（防止短路或故障下电流过大冲击损坏）</b>
				</p>
			</text>
		</region>
		<region region-id="1886" left="192" top="6441.75" width="110.25" height="14.25" align-x="257.25" align-y="6450" show-border="false" show-highlight="false" is-protected="true" z-order="0" background-color="inherit" tag="">
			<math optimize="false" disable-calc="false">
				<ml:eval placeholderMultiplicationStyle="default" xmlns:ml="http://schemas.mathsoft.com/math30">
					<ml:apply>
						<ml:mult/>
						<ml:id xml:space="preserve" subscript="mos_rms">I</ml:id>
						<ml:real>3</ml:real>
					</ml:apply>
